snippet.title: Voidblazers | Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Voidblazers is a story-driven shoot 'em up game for Playdate. Join the crew of Icarus in traveling across the galaxy, battling various fleets, and crossing paths with new friends and enemies on your daring mission. 🪐

Launching Summer of '23. ✨

https://tkers.itch.io/voidblazers
